books.title: To Kill a Mockingbird
books.author: Harper Lee
books.description: A novel about the serious issues of rape and racial inequality, set in the 1930s American South.

books.title: The Great Gatsby
books.author: F. Scott Fitzgerald

books.title: Moby Dick
books.author: Herman Melville
books.description: An epic tale of the voyage of the whaling ship Pequod and its captain, Ahab, who is obsessed with pursuing the giant white whale Moby Dick.
